io.sphere.sdk.carts

Interface LineItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Custom, LineItemLike

    public interface LineItem
extends LineItemLike

    A line item is a snapshot of a product variant at the time it was added to the cart.

    A LineItem can have custom fields.

    See Also:
    AddLineItem, RemoveLineItem, ChangeLineItemQuantity, Order.getLineItems(), Cart.getLineItems()
